==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Dispensatory
<hw>Dis*pen"sa*to*ry</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Dispensatories</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <def>A book or medicinal
formulary containing a systematic description of drugs, and of
preparations made from them. It is usually, but not always,
distinguished from a pharmacop⟦oe⟧ia in that it issued by private
parties, and not by an official body or by government.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dispense</ent>⟦br⟧
